comments: O'Neale (BKN) steps forward as he defends the pass and marginal body contact occurs with Johnson (PHX).
Ayton (PHX) has his right arm extended and makes contact to Irving's (BKN) arms, causing him to lose control of the ball after he has gathered.
Curry (BKN) moves into Lee's (PHX) path and initiates body contact that affects the jump shot attempt.
Irving (BKN) releases the pass before planting his foot on the floor for a third step.
Irving (BKN) is moving alongside Bridges' (PHX) path and marginal body contact occurs with his forearm as they come together during the drive.
Claxton (BKN) holds down Ayton's (PHX) left arm and affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
O'Neale (BKN) moves alongside Lee's (PHX) path and marginal body contact occurs as they engage during the drive.
Lee (PHX) makes contact with the ball and any contact with Curry's (BKN) hand on the ball is considered incidental.
Harris (BKN) commits a take foul on Johnson (PHX).
Johnson (PHX) briefly engages with Curry (BKN), who moves through the contact unimpeded.
Claxton (BKN) commits a take foul on Lee (PHX).
Irving (BKN) reaches in and initiates arm contact with Bridges (PHX) that affects his SQBR.
Wainright (PHX) swipes down and initiates arm contact with Claxton (BKN) that affects his SQBR.
Claxton's (BKN) free throw attempt does not touch the rim.
Harris (BKN) slides his hand off of Johnson's (PHX) side as he defends the pass and marginal contact occurs as Johnson secures the ball.
Claxton (BKN) commits a take foul on Johnson (PHX).
